Package org.tensorics.core.tree.domain

Class AbstractDeferredExpression<R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tensorics.core.tree.domain.AbstractDeferredExpression<R>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - the type of the resolved value of the expression.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Expression<R>, Node
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnalysisExpression, AssertionExpression, BinaryOperationExpression, BinaryPredicateExpression, BinaryPredicateIterableExpression, ConversionOperationExpression, CreationOperationExpression, FunctionalExpression, IterableExpressionToIterable, IterableResolvingExpression, PickExpression, Placeholder, PredicateExpression, UnaryOperationExpression
    public abstract class AbstractDeferredExpression<R>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Expression<R>
    A base class for all kind of deferred (unresolved) expressions. All the methods of the expression interface are implemented here and cannot be overridden. However, the subclasses can / have to provide the necessary informations for the corresponding resolvers.
